{"tid":664419,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四驅車衝入酒店撞扶手梯","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T06:55:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a87b2a57a85e99ecdea84980191c252e8e70b346","tid":664419,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390032&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fblzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=bbe1074c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180514%2F20390032&h=f7424ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180514/20390032</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月14日 <br />\n<br />\n四驅車衝入酒店撞扶手梯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180514/large/14la5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F14la5p4.jpg&h=dc604967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■四驅車撞毀酒店扶手電梯，玻璃碎片散滿一地。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一部城巴昨日下午沿着灣仔軒尼詩道行駛，其間與一輛四驅車相撞，四驅車被撞後，繼而失控衝入一間酒店，撞毀酒店門口的扶手電梯；幸好當時扶手梯上並未有乘客，事件中四驅車女司機輕傷，需送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女司機受傷送院<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午3時許，45歲姓柯男車長駕駛城巴沿灣仔軒尼詩道西行，當巴士駛至莊士敦道交界的時候，一輛四驅車由蘭杜街左轉駛入莊士敦道後駛至軒尼詩道；疑四驅車未有在讓線減速慢駛，直駛出來，結果與城巴相撞。<br />\n<br />\n由於撞擊猛烈，四驅車繼而失控，並且鏟上行人路，其後更衝入一間酒店，然後再撞毀位於酒店門口的扶手電梯，扶手電梯的玻璃登時爆裂並散落地上。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，四驅車的右邊車頭損毀，而扶手電梯的玻璃碎片則散滿一地；消息指當時幸好未有乘客使用有關扶手電梯，否則後果堪虞。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報後到達現場，涉事的56歲四驅車女司機在現場協助警方調查，她受了輕傷，事後被送往律敦治醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，城巴車長則沒有受傷。警方現在正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n■記者簡明恩  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n男女大學生公園「打野戰」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n院舍界：增人均面積或減30%宿位"},{"pid":"22829357e89867779804a7ae05f4b777c60a9fa8","tid":664419,"uid":77461,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"女司機"},{"pid":"c5b877c23ee49265fc1ac795501fd952fdd89f81","tid":664419,"uid":36964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:27:57.000Z","msg":"屌! 未入黎已經諗緊係咪女司機!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0ed6681bfbd36e6a693c8a0e1e67ac31feeaf0","tid":664419,"uid":9777,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/132826_1b7adb5f466cc62db656aa51d317263d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F132826_1b7adb5f466cc62db656aa51d317263d.png&h=3d2339e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一眼睇標題以為呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636474cefe145c1171c078080292eb119cacc79b","tid":664419,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"保險唔包要賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d02a0b114f89e9ac44f47653b71949ed43aa8f","tid":664419,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"要賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71486ef23c226ba2ed10414441849ad39004b8c9","tid":664419,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"56歲四驅車<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女司機</span>"},{"pid":"07dbc64af575bef0580f5fc77f4654c68e8e0c23","tid":664419,"uid":55914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"570898cb4